{
  "stem": "21089.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they ask me more about myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was telling him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I am here in charge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Therefore, I know about the ducks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they told me that they are from this unit from the barracks, because not far away they had a depot barracks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was-- they had all arsenal, and the troops which have convoys which have been going east.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had been, like, a point, stop point, and going the other way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I said, no, you cannot go to your base.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I invite them inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the beginning, they are a little leery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I assure them that nobody is their enemy here, because we are all here working on-- and I made scrambled eggs, and fresh bread, and butter, and whisky.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I tell them, we have only moonshine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We don't have any good whiskey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Next time, they brought whiskey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But-- and they were-- next the morning, they came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's three of them, next day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But they had four guns.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they gave me-- and this is for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I said, I am not allowed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I said, when the Lithuanians will come, they will arrest me here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They-- to this respect, the Lithuanian were so suspicious of anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so most of times, they was coming drunk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "One evening, they came, and went through the whole hut.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And here on the wall were-- I don't remember how many-- hats, winter hats, for Sunday hat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And said, how many people are you here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said three of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The two boys, and I am sleeping here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, they argue that more people here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where are you hiding those people?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who they are?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For a long time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, finally, they said, you see how many hats here?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There are more than three of you-- philosophy.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
